                     <interp inst="t17700117-2-verdict10" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder40s"></interp>
               Guilty. 39 s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>(M.) He was a second time indicted for <rs id="t17700117-2-off11" type="offenceDescription">
