                     <interp inst="t17700117-2-off11" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing a silver hilted sword, value 5 l. and a silk belt, value 5 s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t17700117-2-person46">
                        Francis
                         Roberts
                     <interp inst="t17700117-2-person46" type="surname" value="Roberts"></interp>
